		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Oh. Since the platform code took me many hours to do, here is the fix to use if anybody wants it. I can share my other ASM fixes, too. If anyone wants them. What I did was optimize 2 codes which gave me over 50 free bytes! Here is the code. The new portions I noted with my name:<br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">SetCollisionFlag:<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;ldx ObjectOffset&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;pha ;shane<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; lda Player_Y_HighPos ;shane<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; cmp #$01 ;shane<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; bne platfix ;shane<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; lda Player_Y_Position ;shane<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; cmp #$df ;shane<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; bcc platfix ;shane<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; pla ;shane<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; rts ;shane<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; platfix: ;shane<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; pla&nbsp; &nbsp;;shane<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; sta PlatformCollisionFlag,x<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; lda #$00<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; sta Player_State<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; rts<br /></div>

		

