ed to have different attributes. Originally, Worlds A-C were counted as 1-3 and World D as 8. Not anymore. So you are free to define what kind of spring to use where, what Bowser will look like when &quot;fire-balled&quot;, add or minus features from Hard Mode, etc. <br /><br />Enjoy. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_wink.gif" alt=";)" title="Wink" /><br />--ShaneM

		

